            "answer_text": "Great school but concentrates more on studies and less in sports. Has not so great teachers and not so good environment. School lacks in infrastructure but has good results. Had more number of A1 in class 10 and class 12 exams in Kerala because worthy students apply for the school, and secure good grades. So i cant say their success is due to the teachers but themselves. But the teachers are well informed about the pattern and procedure of academics and students are regularly updated on every aspects of the curriculum. One of the best school in Kerala. SAPS is also good but are bit hard on students. Go to placid. ",
